title: Jagadguru Shankaracharya Sri Sri Bharati Tirtha Mahaswamiji and Jagadg...
description: Jagadguru Shankaracharya Sri Sri Bharati Tirtha Mahaswamiji and Jagadguru Sri Sri Vidhushekhara Bharati Mahaswamiji gracing the evening Sabha at the Sri Sringeri Shankara Math, Varanasi. The event marked the culmination of the annual Chaturmasya Vrata observances. #Sringeri #Shankaracharya #Varanasi
